The '''''Tenebrous''''' was a [[Unidentified warship class (Sith Empire)]] of the [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|Sith Empire]] that served as the base of the remnants of [[Imperial Intelligence (Sith Empire)|Imperial Intelligence]] during [[Cipher Nine]]'s efforts to bring down the [[Star Cabal]]. Operating illegally after the dissolution of Imperial Intelligence, Imperial military databases contained no crew or mission records for the ship.

